{
  "stem": "26465.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was-- she had a Serbian guy who also worked for her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Serbian guy was very nice man about 45 or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he also said, you would-- you would be better if you stay in the fields.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't show yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they both decided that I should be staying in the fields most of the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only came home at night under the cover of the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked in the-- in her fields.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at night, I was coming and staying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she had a little room upstairs, like in the attic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she had two little girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- Ania, what was the discussion with the people you stayed with, either there or in Gablinger, in the farm?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was-- what did they know about what was going on in the war?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the camps, specifically?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These people-- these people were somehow negating it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These people could not believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were saying, the German Reich, or nation, needs people to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since we are the-- we have acquired this part of the-- of the country, we have the rights to employ some of the people for the time being.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the war you are going to go back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything will be fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I told them but not everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I just didn't want to sort of aggravate that person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She might not believe me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then she might be hostile to me and might even tell me move out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no they didn't-- certainly that's the one thing that they would never mention and never-- I don't know whether-- I don't think they knew about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
